<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l22">der Gemeine cʒü Jnchenhofen / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_75_r3l23"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / vns het einer bey ew geſeʒʒen genant <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Sneıd<ex>er</ex></expan> / <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l24"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> habe <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> einer genant <expan>W<ex>er</ex>nher</expan> <expan>Lawffemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l25">ſelig <expan>gelaſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat /. vnd darauf <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jm wider / daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l26">drey vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> v̈ber die er klagt / darvmb cʒerede geſecʒet vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l27">ſie ſeinen brief <expan>höre<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mitnamen / Stephan Schüler </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l28"><expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> holper vnd f . Steimpach / vnd daʒ vns die <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l29">heten / daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>nher</expan> <expan>lawffemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> ein redlıch geſchefte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l30">getan vnd <expan>dıſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dreÿ <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>cʒevormund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geſecʒet het </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l31">vnd daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">d </del> heten ſie awſgerıcht vnd domit getan / als ſein </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_76" id="37v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l1">geſcheftbrıef <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> deʒ Gerichts <expan>Jnſıg<ex>el</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> awſweiſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l2">vnd <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Sneıder ſchon <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / was er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l3">Jm geſchıkt het / des ſie auch einen quitbrief <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l4">Gerichts Jnſıgel <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd daʒ ſie <expan>maint<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l5">Jm nıchts mer ſchuldig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> /. vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſc</expan></del> wir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l6">dar cʒü nemlıch / daʒ des <expan>lawffemberg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> güts nichts auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l7"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> hawſe lege / Dann dewcht den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Sneıder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l8">daʒ er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> dreyen <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l9">noch ıht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het / <expan>Dar<ex>vmb</ex></expan> <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l10"><expan>ſcheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt / <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogen<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſlewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l11"><expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> vor deʒ Reıchs <expan>Richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l12">vvir deʒ ermant <expan>würd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſo <expan>dıſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü den er cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l13"><expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het anheim <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> / wolt er ſich <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l14"><expan>beklage<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bekümern / Daran tet er vns vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l15"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vngütlich / . Nu hat er vns / aber einen brief geſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l16">vnd ſchreibt vns vil <expan>ſelcʒeim<ex>er</ex></expan> teyding / als wir ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l17">ſeins briefs den er vns <expan>yecʒund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geſant hat ein abſchrıft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l18">ſchicken <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> in <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jn daran </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l19">vveıſen 
<del rend="strikethrough">weıſen </del> wöllet / daʒ er vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l20">ſıch <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache v̈berhebe / vnd dunk Jn / daʒ er cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l21">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / daʒ er ſich darvmb an <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l22"><expan>frewntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>benüge<ex>n</ex></expan> laʒʒ / des wir Jm von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l23"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / als wir ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> yecʒunden / vnd auch / Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l24"><expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd laſſet vns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l25"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vvıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthonij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_75" id="37r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den bescheiden lewten, den geswornen der gemeine czü Inchenhofen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns het einer, bey ew gesezzen, genant
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Sneid<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> habe <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, einer genant <expan>W<ex>er</ex>nher</expan>
<expan>Lawffemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> selig,
                            <expan>gelasse<ex>n</ex></expan> hat. Und darauf
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im wider, daz wir
                        drey unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, über die er klagt, darumb czerede
                        geseczet und sie seinen brief <expan>höre<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mitnamen Stephan Schüler,
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Holper und <expan cert="unknown">F.</expan> Steimpach, und daz uns die <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        heten, daz <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>W<ex>er</ex>nher</expan>
<expan>Lawffemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> ein redlich geschefte getan und
                                <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> drey
                            <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>czevormund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geseczet het; und daz heten sie
                        awsgericht und domit getan, als sein <pb facs="#facs_76" id="37v"/>gescheftbrief
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan> dez gerichts
                            <expan>insig<ex>el</ex></expan> czü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
                        awsweise, und <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Sneider schon <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        was er im geschikt het, des sie auch einen quitbrief
                            <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan> des gerichts insigel
                            <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und daz sie
